trans-unit.source: Defines an entity type that exposes an entity key.
This interface is used to expose the entity key to Object Services.
trans-unit.target: Essa interface é usada para expor a chave da entidade para os serviços de objetos.

trans-unit.source: Object Services uses the <xref:System.Data.Objects.DataClasses.IEntityWithKey.EntityKey%2A> property to manage objects in the object context.
trans-unit.target: Objeto serviços usam o <xref:System.Data.Objects.DataClasses.IEntityWithKey.EntityKey%2A> propriedade para gerenciar objetos no contexto do objeto.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Identity Resolution, State Management, and Change Tracking](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bd49311-0e72-4ea4-8355-38fe57036ba0) and [Tracking Changes in POCO Entities](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/52d2fc77-5c87-4082-a8e2-a2952ceb8461).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [resolução de identidade, gerenciamento de estado e controle de alterações](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bd49311-0e72-4ea4-8355-38fe57036ba0) e [de controle de alterações em entidades POCO](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/52d2fc77-5c87-4082-a8e2-a2952ceb8461).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Data.EntityKey" /> for instances of entity types that implement this interface.
The <see cref="T:System.Data.EntityKey" /> for instances of entity types that implement this interface.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Data.EntityKey" /> para instâncias de tipos de entidade que implementam esta interface.

trans-unit.source: Object Services uses the <xref:System.Data.Objects.DataClasses.IEntityWithKey.EntityKey%2A> property to manage objects in the object context.
